Events.Text: Hello! I need some directons today.

Scenario.UserTask: You want directions from 'Forbes and Murray' to 'Broadway and Main' at 8 pm by Transit. When the wizard gives the 1st and 4th step, indicate that you do not understand until you are given more detail. Keep going until you've reached your destination.
Scenario.WizardTask: Tell the user the directions from their departure location to their arrival location
